Currently, tm_name is either "LOCAL" or "Etc/UTC", due to std/times only returning those two.

Some note about implement details the different between std/times and Python's times

std/times DateTime's utcOffset is opposed to struct_time.tm_gmtoff e.g. in the east, DateTime.utcOffset is negative.
